{"tid":97654,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"歐遊半年，你問我答","createTime":"2017-01-27T19:38:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-30T20:32:28.000Z","uid":27849,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d922eba27a6a078b0023402f9cd624c6a8336b96","tid":97654,"uid":27849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T19:38:42.000Z","msg":"為左紀念一年前嘅今日，我飛左去Exchange，決定開個你問我答緬懷下當年歐遊經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n半年黎我留係返學地方既時間應該2個月都冇，曬撚晒啲租<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大概去過：<br />\n西班牙、葡萄牙、斯洛"},{"pid":"ae4f348056908fccb7577969abf90ff1e70d44d1","tid":97654,"uid":27849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T19:46:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>為左紀念一年前嘅今日，我飛左去Exchange，決定開個你問我答緬懷下當年歐遊經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n半年黎我留係返學地方既時間應該2個月都冇，曬撚晒啲租<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大概去過：<br />\n西班牙、葡萄牙<br />\n斯洛文尼亞、克羅地亞<br />\n捷克、匈牙利、奧地利、斯洛伐克<br />\n波蘭、烏克蘭<br />\n意大利（自駕）、馬爾他（自駕）<br />\n冰島<br />\n荷蘭、比利時<br />\n<br />\n另外仲有london, Paris, Copenhagen, Cologne, Munich <br />\n<br />\n試過couchsurfing，都有唔少地方係獨遊<br />\n過年返左大陸悶悶地，希望有人陪我吹下水啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </blockquote><br />\n自<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n未打完㩒錯制post左"},{"pid":"3b623316e4aa58355283555ba305439084583d15","tid":97654,"uid":13534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T19:50:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>為左紀念一年前嘅今日，我飛左去Exchange，決定開個你問我答緬懷下當年歐遊經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n半年黎我留係返學地方既時間應該2個月都冇，曬撚晒啲租<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大概去過：<br />\n西班牙、葡萄牙<br />\n斯洛文尼亞、克羅地亞<br />\n捷克、匈牙利、奧地利、斯洛伐克<br />\n波蘭、烏克蘭<br />\n意大利（自駕）、馬爾他（自駕）<br />\n冰島<br />\n荷蘭、比利時<br />\n<br />\n另外仲有london, Paris, Copenhagen, Cologne, Munich <br />\n<br />\n試過couchsurfing，都有唔少地方係獨遊<br />\n過年返左大陸悶悶地，希望有人陪我吹下水啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </blockquote><br />\n自<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n未打完㩒錯制post左</blockquote><br />\n大部份都去過 克羅地亞同greece  真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cfa24b6afe8fac3988bd4d5a75b6037e3b9673c","tid":97654,"uid":27849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T19:53:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n大部份都去過 克羅地亞同greece  真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好掛住瘋狂旅行嘅日子<br />\n坐係街邊曬下太陽飲杯野又一個下奏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7e1417f574d294f007553d71042ee0ad8989401","tid":97654,"uid":28622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T20:01:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0sHB927.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0sHB927.jpg&h=5a349ac4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴黎JJ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e21c1ef9739a2e376a2e1aa0dc762cd85b30a954","tid":97654,"uid":27849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T20:10:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴黎JJ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打依嫁係巴黎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d714358e32bc31fb9199f580d0ecb70f6b44c668","tid":97654,"uid":28622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T20:47:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴黎JJ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打依嫁係巴黎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  巴打你都係？"},{"pid":"924be16456b77870842f6485975c2608f81fbe28","tid":97654,"uid":67113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T20:48:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0683bc95366115ef3d07e1022eec82ca4dc8b3d3","tid":97654,"uid":26823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T23:02:17.000Z","msg":"波蘭同芬蘭去幾多日好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋推薦邊d cities??"},{"pid":"809f74a98adb8730509e6d53040f394da8507a29","tid":97654,"uid":33242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T05:06:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"642c945b7f524f6493d8ff002a4d862d264a662b","tid":97654,"uid":33242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T05:08:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1d4ab92bd4d62c5ff5e57eca9604de1084465907","tid":97654,"uid":57774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T05:40:54.000Z","msg":"想問下巴打<br />\n黎緊5月頭會去西葡<br />\n9:00 arrive Barcelona total 3日&gt; 第三晚night bus to Madrid &gt; Madrid 1day + 2 days for Segovia Toledo day trip &gt; Cordoba 2-3day &gt; Granada 2-3day&gt; Malaga  1day ( Ronda day trip) &gt; Sevilla 2-3 day 第3晚night bus to Lisbon&gt; 3 days Lisbon 包埋 Sinatra + Cabo da roca&gt; 第三日1430飛<br />\n<br />\n會唔會太趕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00855430831b90ad6ca39c769095d893666e2aaf","tid":97654,"uid":7796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T05:53:11.000Z","msg":"巴打想問下意大利自駕安唔安全？<br />\n我係日本揸過600幾公里路<br />\n夠唔夠應付<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可唔可以分享下意大利自駕<br />\nBtw我得21歲<br />\n有無影響？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b49ade63b2993665d14468c161bcc5160e216a9f","tid":97654,"uid":27849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T07:27:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  巴打你都係？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n返左地獄鬼國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好掛住外國嘅生活"},{"pid":"6834084b07c28db4c42cc1c54f96cc77d1544180","tid":97654,"uid":27849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T07:28:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一共洗左幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇計阿<br />\n我冇點就住洗，我諗連埋機票都7-8萬<br />\n因為仲有exchange屋租同水電個啲<br />\n不過學校連政府比左5.5萬sponsor"},{"pid":"ae34ee7ed6374ea6b66ef53d502c99156a37cd14","tid":97654,"uid":11525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T07:33:54.000Z","msg":"匈牙利同奧地利值唔值得去？<br />\n有咩推介？<br />\n兩個女仔去的話會唔會危險？<br />\n唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12b2b65de0415c487c8e8240a9861cac6b9f1330","tid":97654,"uid":27849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T07:36:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>波蘭同芬蘭去幾多日好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋推薦邊d cities??</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我淨係去左波蘭嘅krakow咋 <br />\n但我做research個陣見佢啲海邊城市好似幾靚<br />\nKrakow嘅話可以留2-3晚，主要行市內同集中營 <br />\n集中營<span style=\"font-size: large;\">一定要book!!!</span><br />\n唔book就要早去等後補位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外我自己就冇去鹽礦 但fd講如果成班fd可以一齊join miner route，佢地話好玩<br />\n<br />\n我覺得長有長玩短有短玩既，起碼預2星期啦<br />\n如果我有時間，會揀飛krakow一路玩埋波羅的海三國上芬蘭（或者調轉）"},{"pid":"d3e1697cccda674af13d47ab44a199edaf6c078c","tid":97654,"uid":27849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T07:56:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你條路線係點?<br />\n多數撘飛機定火車?</blockquote><br />\n邊個國家推薦留耐少少?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n多手未打完就send左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為我係去exchange，所以係分別去左幾個trip咁<br />\nTrip內就盡量巴士，但其實搭ryanair都幾平 <br />\n我係東歐個邊飛西班牙都係20歐左右<br />\n<br />\n國家既話，我鐘意葡萄牙，仲有冰島、荷蘭（！！）同Slovenia，如果我有錢都會想去挪威<br />\n<br />\n葡萄牙啲人幾好，而且啲野好好食！我日日狂啪葡撻同正宗豬扒包<br />\n冰島好靚唔洗講啦，如果我識揸車一定會自駕環島再露營（當然要夏天先做到）<br />\n荷蘭好舒服，除左可以日日stoned之外，如果厭羊角村太遠可以去下Edam, volendam, marken一日遊。去完會反問自己，點解我要住係香港咁辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"355a51eb746ccd563ff1b9ef1ba80f7fc39ac0a2","tid":97654,"uid":27849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T08:02:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>匈牙利同奧地利值唔值得去？<br />\n有咩推介？<br />\n兩個女仔去的話會唔會危險？<br />\n唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n絕對唔會！！！！！！<br />\n點解？<br />\n因為我都係兩個女仔去！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我覺得budapest同hallstatt都幾靚阿！不過係budapest望住條橋，會好想隔離個個係男朋友而唔係個fd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外呢條路線可以去埋slovakia首都Bratislava，個到冇乜野玩，但因為架巴士都一定經呢個城市，可以stay一晚玩埋。個城堡同舊城區都幾靚，仲有個全藍色既教堂"},{"pid":"810ddf2e4978f1012827a1dca1fdb6a5d7b63a15","tid":97654,"uid":27849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T08:09:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問下巴打<br />\n黎緊5月頭會去西葡<br />\n9:00 arrive Barcelona total 3日&amp;gt; 第三晚night bus to Madrid &amp;gt; Madrid 1day + 2 days for Segovia Toledo day trip &amp;gt; Cordoba 2-3day &amp;gt; Granada 2-3day&amp;gt; Malaga  1day ( Ronda day trip) &amp;gt; Sevilla 2-3 day 第3晚night bus to Lisbon&amp;gt; 3 days Lisbon 包埋 Sinatra + Cabo da roca&amp;gt; 第三日1430飛<br />\n<br />\n會唔會太趕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得有啲趕，因為有時你預stay 3日，但扣返搭巴士啲時間可能就得返2日甚至一日半。同埋去到一半你應該就會好崩潰唔想再早起，可能我個人比較懶啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但我會suggest sevilla同granada都要留3日，因為都幾值得行"},{"pid":"dd6dbdb227f705a54ee69eb0ae5e95a861cb0f1c","tid":97654,"uid":9412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T08:11:34.000Z","msg":"有咩最遺憾冇做到"},{"pid":"60d751635c4b54cdc8e7e652ed4475fe7af587ad","tid":97654,"uid":74775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T08:13:23.000Z","msg":"阿姆斯特丹去德國近唔近？"},{"pid":"cdb7159d00a1708e1649827c1ba464f0c495ee83","tid":97654,"uid":27849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T08:16:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打想問下意大利自駕安唔安全？<br />\n我係日本揸過600幾公里路<br />\n夠唔夠應付<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可唔可以分享下意大利自駕<br />\nBtw我得21歲<br />\n有無影響？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n安全都幾安全嘅！我覺得意大利自駕最爽係揸上Dolomites呢類大自然嘅地方玩，仲有Tuscany呢堆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但如果你只係去Florence, Rome, Venice呢類大路嘅歷史城市，我絕對<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔建議自駕！！</span><br />\n因為佢地好多地方都唔比外地車入，但佢唔會有牌攔住，只有一個好陰濕嘅意大利文路牌，一但你轉左入去又比cam影到，就即刻罰錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  勁撚易中伏<br />\n<br />\n但如果去Dolomites嘅話，你要諗下你有冇信心揸山路，因為有啲路都幾危，但我個陣係老豆揸，佢就車手上身揸到勁撚興奮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋21歲租車要貴啲"},{"pid":"b4a3babf055b5d7743e2b8fd4d189a24612db61f","tid":97654,"uid":27849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T08:18:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有咩最遺憾冇做到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇溝鬼妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a2cd5dcb5993473f389e058bb0cebe8310b3190","tid":97654,"uid":27849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T08:19:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>阿姆斯特丹去德國近唔近？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你想去德國邊先？搭megabus去cologne好似6-8個鐘"},{"pid":"e4eb28eae25da3dba3cf88755872a1f6f3b92fb9","tid":97654,"uid":28622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T09:02:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  巴打你都係？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n返左地獄鬼國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好掛住外國嘅生活</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我有少少掛住香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df6272f1ad172ef7518643b72fbb82811537b1a3","tid":97654,"uid":563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T09:12:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一共洗左幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇計阿<br />\n我冇點就住洗，我諗連埋機票都7-8萬<br />\n因為仲有exchange屋租同水電個啲<br />\n不過學校連政府比左5.5萬sponsor</blockquote><br />\n巴打連埋屋租水電先係7,8萬？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1960e05784716ea95e940254184dd36b4fcc32e8","tid":97654,"uid":27849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T09:55:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一共洗左幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇計阿<br />\n我冇點就住洗，我諗連埋機票都7-8萬<br />\n因為仲有exchange屋租同水電個啲<br />\n不過學校連政府比左5.5萬sponsor</blockquote><br />\n巴打連埋屋租水電先係7,8萬？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為我去東歐國家 我間房月租250歐咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ce1f19e9d5477e72928ba3abae78fc1961d57f3","tid":97654,"uid":57774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T15:20:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想問下巴打<br />\n黎緊5月頭會去西葡<br />\n9:00 arrive Barcelona total 3日&amp;amp;gt; 第三晚night bus to Madrid &amp;amp;gt; Madrid 1day + 2 days for Segovia Toledo day trip &amp;amp;gt; Cordoba 2-3day &amp;amp;gt; Granada 2-3day&amp;amp;gt; Malaga  1day ( Ronda day trip) &amp;amp;gt; Sevilla 2-3 day 第3晚night bus to Lisbon&amp;amp;gt; 3 days Lisbon 包埋 Sinatra + Cabo da roca&amp;amp;gt; 第三日1430飛<br />\n<br />\n會唔會太趕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得有啲趕，因為有時你預stay 3日，但扣返搭巴士啲時間可能就得返2日甚至一日半。同埋去到一半你應該就會好崩潰唔想再早起，可能我個人比較懶啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但我會suggest sevilla同granada都要留3日，因為都幾值得行</blockquote><br />\nGranada 個皇宮你朝早定晏就去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9777a0b8b972d6d82adb842f2fc6795db5e62a41","tid":97654,"uid":11525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T15:49:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>匈牙利同奧地利值唔值得去？<br />\n有咩推介？<br />\n兩個女仔去的話會唔會危險？<br />\n唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n絕對唔會！！！！！！<br />\n點解？<br />\n因為我都係兩個女仔去！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我覺得budapest同hallstatt都幾靚阿！不過係budapest望住條橋，會好想隔離個個係男朋友而唔係個fd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外呢條路線可以去埋slovakia首都Bratislava，個到冇乜野玩，但因為架巴士都一定經呢個城市，可以stay一晚玩埋。個城堡同舊城區都幾靚，仲有個全藍色既教堂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我同朋友會喺英國去瑞士、匈牙利同奧地利<br />\nHallstatt一定會去！睇相見到啲風景好靚<br />\n但匈牙利冇咩特別留意，<br />\n本身想去埋斯洛伐克、布拉格<br />\n但夾唔到時間<br />\n<br />\nBtw想問下有咩野食好食<br />\n唔該巴打！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61111b0114dd19ca0a063bbb984148c5bdcab36c","tid":97654,"uid":53880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T16:16:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想問下巴打<br />\n黎緊5月頭會去西葡<br />\n9:00 arrive Barcelona total 3日&amp;gt; 第三晚night bus to Madrid &amp;gt; Madrid 1day + 2 days for Segovia Toledo day trip &amp;gt; Cordoba 2-3day &amp;gt; Granada 2-3day&amp;gt; Malaga  1day ( Ronda day trip) &amp;gt; Sevilla 2-3 day 第3晚night bus to Lisbon&amp;gt; 3 days Lisbon 包埋 Sinatra + Cabo da roca&amp;gt; 第三日1430飛<br />\n<br />\n會唔會太趕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得有啲趕，因為有時你預stay 3日，但扣返搭巴士啲時間可能就得返2日甚至一日半。同埋去到一半你應該就會好崩潰唔想再早起，可能我個人比較懶啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但我會suggest sevilla同granada都要留3日，因為都幾值得行</blockquote><br />\n可唔可以講下sevilla同granada有咩景點同節目值去?<br />\n去sevilla有冇去埋ronda?"},{"pid":"f40a795e4b84b774b847a686883f477baa057b9e","tid":97654,"uid":75495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T16:45:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想問下巴打<br />\n黎緊5月頭會去西葡<br />\n9:00 arrive Barcelona total 3日&amp;amp;gt; 第三晚night bus to Madrid &amp;amp;gt; Madrid 1day + 2 days for Segovia Toledo day trip &amp;amp;gt; Cordoba 2-3day &amp;amp;gt; Granada 2-3day&amp;amp;gt; Malaga  1day ( Ronda day trip) &amp;amp;gt; Sevilla 2-3 day 第3晚night bus to Lisbon&amp;amp;gt; 3 days Lisbon 包埋 Sinatra + Cabo da roca&amp;amp;gt; 第三日1430飛<br />\n<br />\n會唔會太趕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得有啲趕，因為有時你預stay 3日，但扣返搭巴士啲時間可能就得返2日甚至一日半。同埋去到一半你應該就會好崩潰唔想再早起，可能我個人比較懶啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但我會suggest sevilla同granada都要留3日，因為都幾值得行</blockquote><br />\n可唔可以講下sevilla同granada有咩景點同節目值去?<br />\n去sevilla有冇去埋ronda?</blockquote><br />\n我上年10月去左西葡16日, 路線係咁:<br />\nBarcelona 4日 -&gt; ryanair去Seville 3日 -&gt;火車上Madrid 3日 -&gt;ryanair去Porto 3日 -&gt;火車落Lisbon 3日<br />\n<br />\n我覺得Barcelona 3日都得, Seville 分別去Cordoba 同Ronda day trip都得, Madrid 市內好悶 都係去Segovia 同Toledo day trip, Porto好正個人覺得多野睇過Lisbon, Lisbon就都係Sinatra + Cabo da roca一日搞掂"},{"pid":"685e639ccacbccac20a65e7927f4cf2b2a260d90","tid":97654,"uid":27849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T17:44:18.000Z","msg":"邊個偷偷地留低負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2ae81836759ec77ac3822a5d21ac7d33daf857c","tid":97654,"uid":27849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T17:48:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\nGranada 個皇宮你朝早定晏就去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唉屌唔好提<br />\n由於本人太懶冇做好功課，搞到去到granada先知原來皇宮booking已經full到下個月<br />\n<br />\n之後唯有同hostel d人約好要四點一齊起身上山排隊<br />\n點知最尾得韓仔一個人上到去，而佢都淨係買到最後兩張<br />\n我六點起身爬到上山就得返花園飛，<br />\n但韓仔話個皇宮其實都同出面差唔多，<br />\n希望佢唔係tum我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3f034fd95bfbd1d9e812ceb883a4c3dd26b4048","tid":97654,"uid":26823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T23:53:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>匈牙利同奧地利值唔值得去？<br />\n有咩推介？<br />\n兩個女仔去的話會唔會危險？<br />\n唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係遲下兩個女仔去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d567333281217a39575c7cba3b8dff39fd4e6fc","tid":97654,"uid":40353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T01:50:50.000Z","msg":"去歐洲點樣防止被人偷野？<br />\n利申，冇去過，聽人講偷竊問題好嚴重"},{"pid":"559431ec7c81eca45a498dedb859abbe00924665","tid":97654,"uid":57774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T02:10:49.000Z","msg":"<bl