e 仲正"},{"pid":"ed50c710ef0bfc139271953646ba58ffec108fc2","tid":97654,"uid":27849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T05:09:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去歐洲點樣防止被人偷野？<br />\n利申，冇去過，聽人講偷竊問題好嚴重</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我開頭買左貼身腰包，但用左幾日就放棄左<br />\n可能我keep住著登山外套個啲，個樣窮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n全程都冇人埋過我身想偷我野<br />\n不過我阿媽係意大利比人開左兩次袋<br />\n<br />\n最重要都係自己提高警覺，唔好掛住玩就唔記得啲財物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"395e8a5403fa8ad03a6ea8ae3f504dbfc3889f57","tid":97654,"uid":27849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T05:13:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\nBtw想問下有咩野食好食<br />\n唔該巴打！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪因爲我窮，我覺得歐洲冇咩野好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除左法國食過啲蝦好甜之外就冇<br />\n<br />\nVienna嘅話好似都係去食ribs of vienna <br />\n同埋去歐洲要瘋狂食雪糕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8a4b844acdef83aa77a7935bd137e45f3545e8d","tid":97654,"uid":27849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T05:15:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>匈牙利同奧地利值唔值得去？<br />\n有咩推介？<br />\n兩個女仔去的話會唔會危險？<br />\n唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你去開東歐咪stay 幾日玩埋 我覺得好安全<br />\nAustria 去Hallstatt <br />\n唔去Hungary 的話 ，Austria 經ck上Prague 仲正</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但我記得奧地利去ck嘅交通有啲麻煩<br />\n你可以checkcheck"},{"pid":"f7fffe1703d1ac5b7b9116bce8bd6436f53433c7","tid":97654,"uid":75495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T05:29:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>匈牙利同奧地利值唔值得去？<br />\n有咩推介？<br />\n兩個女仔去的話會唔會危險？<br />\n唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你去開東歐咪stay 幾日玩埋 我覺得好安全<br />\nAustria 去Hallstatt <br />\n唔去Hungary 的話 ，Austria 經ck上Prague 仲正</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但我記得奧地利去ck嘅交通有啲麻煩<br />\n你可以checkcheck</blockquote><br />\n有ck shuttle / bean shuttle呢D巴士來往Austria 至ck/ Prague<br />\n東歐我自己覺得唔危險, 不過如果匈牙利同捷克揀我建議捷克<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe22f9fc2fdecaf64f853a1e1937880fb8b90168","tid":97654,"uid":75495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T05:31:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\nBtw想問下有咩野食好食<br />\n唔該巴打！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪因爲我窮，我覺得歐洲冇咩野好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除左法國食過啲蝦好甜之外就冇<br />\n<br />\nVienna嘅話好似都係去食ribs of vienna <br />\n同埋去歐洲要瘋狂食雪糕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nVienna都可以去食 Schnitzel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d82629491d7f775edc22da06940fac1f5e85494a","tid":97654,"uid":11525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T07:46:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n你去開東歐咪stay 幾日玩埋 我覺得好安全<br />\nAustria 去Hallstatt <br />\n唔去Hungary 的話 ，Austria 經ck上Prague 仲正</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但我記得奧地利去ck嘅交通有啲麻煩<br />\n你可以checkcheck</blockquote><br />\n有ck shuttle / bean shuttle呢D巴士來往Austria 至ck/ Prague<br />\n東歐我自己覺得唔危險, 不過如果匈牙利同捷克揀我建議捷克<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n捷克有咩玩？<br />\n我自己想去奧地利<br />\n見匈牙利喺附近所以就諗住去埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加上我個朋友已經訂左機票喺匈牙利走"},{"pid":"4b0bccdd9f86aee3b02fad2a4910e32e10478fa3","tid":97654,"uid":57774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T08:01:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但我記得奧地利去ck嘅交通有啲麻煩<br />\n你可以checkcheck</blockquote><br />\n有ck shuttle / bean shuttle呢D巴士來往Austria 至ck/ Prague<br />\n東歐我自己覺得唔危險, 不過如果匈牙利同捷克揀我建議捷克<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n捷克有咩玩？<br />\n我自己想去奧地利<br />\n見匈牙利喺附近所以就諗住去埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加上我個朋友已經訂左機票喺匈牙利走</blockquote><br />\nCk Prague 最出名<br />\n去完東歐 印象最深都係Prague"},{"pid":"ee258adc90856f2206099ad63cbecd3cf552e71a","tid":97654,"uid":53880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T11:52:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去歐洲點樣防止被人偷野？<br />\n利申，冇去過，聽人講偷竊問題好嚴重</blockquote><br />\n意大利情況唔太清楚, 可能比較嚴重<br />\n但西歐普遍小心啲都冇問題<br />\n搭地鐵有得坐低就坐低 冇就背囊放前面 用腳夾住<br />\n去人多地方背囊可以揹番前面或者可以加把鎖<br />\n財物證件跟身就唔洗講. 冬天可以放係外套啲內袋"},{"pid":"26bdb44dcf726249dbaadd4ca3a475a3c97a6286","tid":97654,"uid":53880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T11:54:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想問下巴打<br />\n黎緊5月頭會去西葡<br />\n9:00 arrive Barcelona total 3日&amp;amp;gt; 第三晚night bus to Madrid &amp;amp;gt; Madrid 1day + 2 days for Segovia Toledo day trip &amp;amp;gt; Cordoba 2-3day &amp;amp;gt; Granada 2-3day&amp;amp;gt; Malaga  1day ( Ronda day trip) &amp;amp;gt; Sevilla 2-3 day 第3晚night bus to Lisbon&amp;amp;gt; 3 days Lisbon 包埋 Sinatra + Cabo da roca&amp;amp;gt; 第三日1430飛<br />\n<br />\n會唔會太趕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得有啲趕，因為有時你預stay 3日，但扣返搭巴士啲時間可能就得返2日甚至一日半。同埋去到一半你應該就會好崩潰唔想再早起，可能我個人比較懶啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但我會suggest sevilla同granada都要留3日，因為都幾值得行</blockquote><br />\n可唔可以講下sevilla同granada有咩景點同節目值去?<br />\n去sevilla有冇去埋ronda?</blockquote><br />\n我上年10月去左西葡16日, 路線係咁:<br />\nBarcelona 4日 -&gt; ryanair去Seville 3日 -&gt;火車上Madrid 3日 -&gt;ryanair去Porto 3日 -&gt;火車落Lisbon 3日<br />\n<br />\n我覺得Barcelona 3日都得, Seville 分別去Cordoba 同Ronda day trip都得, Madrid 市內好悶 都係去Segovia 同Toledo day trip, Porto好正個人覺得多野睇過Lisbon, Lisbon就都係Sinatra + Cabo da roca一日搞掂</blockquote><br />\n想知sevilla市內有咩玩 玩到幾日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋係咪有鬥牛睇?"},{"pid":"c4e70d9d8ef6afcb5c3ee66988c683c37352b18a","tid":97654,"uid":75495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T12:28:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想問下巴打<br />\n黎緊5月頭會去西葡<br />\n9:00 arrive Barcelona total 3日&amp;amp;amp;gt; 第三晚night bus to Madrid &amp;amp;amp;gt; Madrid 1day + 2 days for Segovia Toledo day trip &amp;amp;amp;gt; Cordoba 2-3day &amp;amp;amp;gt; Granada 2-3day&amp;amp;amp;gt; Malaga  1day ( Ronda day trip) &amp;amp;amp;gt; Sevilla 2-3 day 第3晚night bus to Lisbon&amp;amp;amp;gt; 3 days Lisbon 包埋 Sinatra + Cabo da roca&amp;amp;amp;gt; 第三日1430飛<br />\n<br />\n會唔會太趕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得有啲趕，因為有時你預stay 3日，但扣返搭巴士啲時間可能就得返2日甚至一日半。同埋去到一半你應該就會好崩潰唔想再早起，可能我個人比較懶啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但我會suggest sevilla同granada都要留3日，因為都幾值得行</blockquote><br />\n可唔可以講下sevilla同granada有咩景點同節目值去?<br />\n去sevilla有冇去埋ronda?</blockquote><br />\n我上年10月去左西葡16日, 路線係咁:<br />\nBarcelona 4日 -&amp;gt; ryanair去Seville 3日 -&amp;gt;火車上Madrid 3日 -&amp;gt;ryanair去Porto 3日 -&amp;gt;火車落Lisbon 3日<br />\n<br />\n我覺得Barcelona 3日都得, Seville 分別去Cordoba 同Ronda day trip都得, Madrid 市內好悶 都係去Segovia 同Toledo day trip, Porto好正個人覺得多野睇過Lisbon, Lisbon就都係Sinatra + Cabo da roca一日搞掂</blockquote><br />\n想知sevilla市內有咩玩 玩到幾日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋係咪有鬥牛睇?</blockquote><br />\nAlcazar, Plaza de Espana, Seville Cathedral 呢D可以睇睇, Parasol 好雞可以skip, 鬥牛我無興趣所以淨係去左個鬥牛場參觀下, 好似4-6月先有場<br />\n仲可以睇場flamenco, 基本上一日搞掂<br />\n最記得就係火車站離個中心區好遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62d3d916411b8983a5e5d8a5fe3b